 href="https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/think-ahead/"
 target="_blank"
 rel="noopener"
 &gt;
 https://terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/think-ahead/
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1 id="think-ahead"&gt;Think ahead&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Worse than being blind, is to see and have no vision.
— Helen Keller&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It is really easy to get bogged down in the details of some work and not recall the purpose of what one is actually doing; thus it is good to pause every now and then and recall &lt;strong&gt;why&lt;/strong&gt; one is pursuing a particular goal.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Work hard</title><link>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/work-hard/</link><pubDate>Sun, 06 May 2007 18:52:08 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/orig/work-hard/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguage.github.io/terencetao/career-advice/zh/work-hard.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;
